original_title: PROGRESS Chapter 23: What A Time To Be Alive!
overview: Back to PROGRESS now, and we go back six months for November 2015’s show: Chapter 23 – What A Time To Be Alive! There are no old men thawing out of a freezer here, but we do have a rare event which included a pre-show, and that match that broke the ring… in the main show opener, too!
title: PROGRESS Chapter 23: What A Time To Be Alive!
